  "title": "🌟 Office Cleaner | Loyang | 5 Days Work Week | Up to $1,400 + AWS + Benefits",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Loyang<br />🗓 <strong>Work Days:</strong> Monday – Friday<br />💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> Up to <strong>$1,400</strong> + AWS + Yearly Increment<br />🕒 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> <strong>7:00 AM – 3:00 PM</strong></p><h2>🧹 <strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Perform general office cleaning</p></li><li><p>Sweeping, mopping, vacuuming, and dusting</p></li><li><p>Dispose of trash and maintain cleanliness of office areas</p></li><li><p>Spot-clean glass panels, glass doors, and windows</p></li><li><p>Clean and sanitize restrooms (toilet bowl, basin, mirrors, fixtures)</p></li><li><p>Carry out any additional duties assigned by the supervisor</p></li></ul><h2>👤 <strong>Requirements:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Able to start work immediately or at short notice</p></li><li><p>Prior cleaning experience is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable, and hardworking</p></li></ul><h2>🎁 <strong>Benefits:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>AWS (13th Month Bonus)</p></li><li><p>Yearly salary increment</p></li><li><p>3-month probation</p></li><li><p>Annual leave: 7 days (up to 14 days with service)<br /></p><p><br />EA License No: 23C1703</p><p>EA Personnel No: R1762582</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p></li></ul>",
